description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'You Are Life Itself — Guided Meditation with Mooji' from the channel Moojiji.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: SATSANG OF THE WEEK
https://mooji.tv/satsang-of-the-week

A beautiful guided meditation with Mooji into the space of pure being. 

“Everything is in place for life to unfold in its natural way. Be aware of this. You are not apart from life, but life itself. 

You are simply here - undivided, whole, complete, happy. Be confirmed in your completeness.”

Sahaja Retreat 
18 September 2016 | Guided Meditation

~

This video is the ‘Satsang of the Week’ for 14 March 2021
